==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Surface loading
<hw>Sur"face load`ing</hw>. <fld>(Aeronautics)</fld> <def>The weight
supported per square unit of surface; the quotient obtained by dividing
the gross weight, in pounds, of a fully loaded flying machine, by the
total area, in square feet, of its supporting surface.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Surfacer</ent>⟦br⟧
